snippet.title: Two Minutes w/ Puny Astronaut
snippet.description:
In Two Minutes we hear from a maker/artist/designer in Dundee about their work in... well, in that exact amount of time! This week it's Puny Astronaut, a games development studio whose work you might have seen in the most recent Abertay Digital Graduate Show. 

Creative Dundee:
http://creativedundee.com/
@Creative_Dundee

Puny Astronaut: 
https://www.punyastronaut.com/
@PunyAstronaut
